snippet.title: Flagsplosion Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/652340/Flagsplosion/
Flagsplosion is a flag identifying endless quizzer with over 600 current flags from around the world. Also featuring 100 Training Levels, Practice Mode, Steam Achievements and Steam Leaderboards.
